An intelligent, AI-powered travel planning application that helps users create personalized itineraries, discover hidden gems, and plan their perfect trips with conversational AI assistance.


Go to the terminal open work directory and run following commands:



```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

```
python travel_planner_ui.py
```

```
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```


